CLOSER.SIGNED:
The servant
for Jesus sake,
Thomas Allen.

DIV2.P:
1. By his Originall or Fountain from whence he springs;
he riseth up out of the Sea, which is amplified by the place of
Johns beholding him; I stood upon the sand of the Sea.

1. They differ in number; John saith, I saw a beast rise out
of the Sea; and then it is said in vers. 11. I beheld another beast;
it is not therefore the same.
